description: Grammy award winning bassist and composer, Stanley Clarke, joined the Rock & Review to talk about the latest viral video and song he was a part of "Spread a Smile."  The video includes 60 international artists, including Clarke's longtime friend Chic Corea.  The video is currently heading towards 11 million views and is meant to provide a positive message in these times.  It also supports the Prevention Resource Center.  Stanley is constantly working on new music and collaborating with some of the top musicians in the industry as a founding member of "Return to Forever."  Watch for music music from the Stanley Clarke Band also!
